\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}Do not enter a room without first knocking and receiving an invitation to come in\
{\listtext	\'95	}Do not walk around the room, examining pictures, while waiting for the hostess\
{\listtext	\'95	}Do not introduce politics, religion, or weighty topics for conversation when making calls\
{\listtext	\'95	}Do not call upon a person in reduced circumstances with a display of wealth, dress, and equipage\
{\listtext	\'95	}Do not tattle. Do not carry gossip from one family to another\
{\listtext	\'95	}Do not, if a gentleman, seat yourself upon the sofa beside the hostess, or in near proximity, unless invited to do so\
{\listtext	\'95	}Do not, if a lady, call upon a gentleman (except officially or professionally) unless he may be a confirmed invalid\
{\listtext	\'95	}Do not take a strange gentleman with you, unless positively certain that his introduction will be received with favor\
